      <title>供应紧张预期推动油价延续上涨势头</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-extend-upward-momentum-expectations-tighter-supply-2024-03-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于俄罗斯减产和俄罗斯炼油厂遇袭导致供应紧张的预期，油价周二有望连续第二天上涨，此前油价上涨超过一美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-extend-upward-momentum-expectations-tighter-supply-2024-03-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 01:54:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
