      <title>Blackstone 旗下的 Crown Resorts 适合持有墨尔本赌场牌照</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/blackstone-owned-crown-resorts-found-fit-hold-melbourne-casino-license-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[博彩监管机构周二表示，黑石集团旗下的皇冠度假村可以保留其墨尔本旗舰赌场的经营许可证，距离该赌场因违反反洗钱法而受到政府监管已有两年多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/blackstone-owned-crown-resorts-found-fit-hold-melbourne-casino-license-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 23:47:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
